264
00:15:26,790 --> 00:15:29,180
Water the plants instead.

265
00:15:33,990 --> 00:15:36,010
I'll take care of it.

266
00:15:44,980 --> 00:15:46,760
Thank you.

267
00:16:08,010 --> 00:16:10,360
- Your credit score is too low.
