268
00:16:10,360 --> 00:16:11,660
We can help you.

269
00:16:11,660 --> 00:16:15,280
I'm offering this because I trust you, Ms. Do.

270
00:16:18,990 --> 00:16:23,300
Wait, they indicted her even with all this?

271
00:17:33,410 --> 00:17:34,910
Gosh.

272
00:17:34,910 --> 00:17:37,210
Why do they always come in when I'm taking a short break

273
00:17:37,210 --> 00:17:38,640
